code: @Override protected HazelcastDefaultEndpoint doCreateEndpoint(String uri, String remaining, Map<String, Object> parameters, HazelcastInstance hzInstance) throws Exception {     final HazelcastSedaConfiguration config = new HazelcastSedaConfiguration().     setProperties(config, parameters).     config.setQueueName(remaining).     HazelcastSedaEndpoint answer = new HazelcastSedaEndpoint(hzInstance, uri, this, config).     return answer. }
